name: Neuro-Symbolic Sudoku Solver
shortDescription: PyTorch implementation for the Neuro-Symbolic Sudoku Solver leveraging the power of Neural Logic Machines (NLM developed by Google). This project applies NLM to more complex Sudoku problem.
longDescription: PyTorch implementation for the Neuro-Symbolic Sudoku Solver leveraging the power of Neural Logic Machines (NLM developed by Google). This project applies NLM to more complex Sudoku problem.
